Ants have to build ant hills which takes time and honey

Ant hills have a certain capacity of Ants

so when ant killer is coming thru, if there are any ants not in an ant hill, they will all die.

New Button in the menu to build anthill, and you place the anthill where you want it.
Construction begins and it is a small light brown circle. Each stage increases its size, and then when it is done, it becomes dark brown.
